title: Microsoft Office 2013 VL ProPlus English (x86-x64) May 2016
description:
*** Release Info

Includes

- Microsoft Office Professional Plus (x86/x64 Volume License en-US)
- Version 15.0.4454.1000 (SP1)
- Integrated updates: May 9, 2016
- Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (activator)
- Visual Studio for Office Runtime (version 10.0.60724), required update
- Optional: Classic Menu for Office v5.85, Office Tab v9.81, Remove/Restore Sign In option (reg file)

*** Installation

- Install Office 2013
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime (add-ins folder)
- Install any of these optional utilities (add-ins folder)

Optional

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 + serial
- Office Tab v9.81 + serial
- Merge reg file Remove/Restore Sign In Office 2013' to remove / restore the Sign in option (reboot required)

*** System requirements

Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2 (64-bit version for Office 64-bit)
